name: Dark waters / Changing my mindset #5
description:
Dark Waters is a series of drawings that attempt to represent states of my mind during meditation processes. They manifest energetic shocks, spatial translations, explosions of color and packets of information that happen in my psyche during transcendent processes. Changing my mindset works the internal transformation process that the flow of new information produces on consciousness.

It was made in Processing and exported with movie maker in MP4 format.

The code used is a fork of Landscape by Henrik Linusson, included in his manual of examples for Processing. You can check it here:
https://github.com/Gornajur/processing-examples/tree/master/landscape
The code of this skecht can be consulted here:
https://github.com/Gornajur/processing-examples/blob/master/Change.pde
